# EMI stuff

btw.anvil.info=The Anvil can be placed anywhere, and it's used for either repair, or enchantment book application. Note: This bypasses the typical limit of Infernal Enchanters.
classicAddon.workbench.info=Crafting table can be placed anywhere. This has vanilla hardness levels. Note: This can burn.
classicAddon.furnace.info=Furnaces can be placed anywhere. This will ignite whenever fuel is supplied, and cooks stuff 4x faster than brick ovens, but also burns fuel 4x faster.
classicAddon.hopper.info=Soulforged Steel Hoppers can be placed anywhere, though it's rather anomalous in its behavior. This thing not only pushes items into containers in a specific direction, unlike wooden hoppers, but also sucks items from the containers above. It may cause anomalies.
