# Config stuff

hunger-system.degranularize-hunger-system=De-granularize The Hunger System
hunger-system.degranularize-hunger-system.desc=Granular hunger system acts like the vanilla hunger system.
hunger-system.modern-exhaustion-values=Modern Exhaustion Values
hunger-system.modern-exhaustion-values.desc=This is best suited for an addon like BTWG.
hunger-system.quick-heal-toggle=Modern Regen. Toggle
hunger-system.quick-heal-toggle.desc=vMC 1.9+ regeneration system. False (Off) by default.
hunger-system.quick-heal-ticks=Ticks until Modern Regen
hunger-system.quick-heal-ticks.desc=How quickly the regen occurs. 20 ticks = 1 second. 10 ticks is vanilla, 40 ticks is Tetro48's suggested value.
hunger-system.hunger-regen-offset-toggle=Offset for health regen from hunger
hunger-system.hunger-regen-offset-toggle.desc=This shifts the regen stop region to be below 8.6 shanks instead of below 9 shanks. This makes regen feel much more consistent, even if internally, it may not exactly match up. Default: True.
difficulty.cursed-difficulty-mode=Cursed Difficulty
difficulty.cursed-difficulty-mode.desc=Unshackle BTW difficulty settings, but marking it cursed. NOTE: If you're seeing this, you're either on LAN, or single player. Changes made through either commands or GUI don't persist, and this requires persistence.
client.new-moon-brightness-level=New Moon Brightness Level
client.new-moon-brightness-level.desc=Purely a visual setting... 0: Pitch black. 1: A tiny bit of light. NOTE: If you're seeing this, you're either on LAN, or single player. If you can change this, you can mess with the host player!
world.gloom-toggle=Gloom Toggle
world.gloom-toggle.desc=Default: False.
world.guaranteed-seed-drop=Guaranteed Crop Seed Drop
world.guaranteed-seed-drop.desc=Crop seeds will always drop, no matter the growth stage, just like in modern vanilla. Default: True.
world.hemp-seed-drop=Hemp Seed chance from Tall Grass
world.hemp-seed-drop.desc=1% drop chance for hemp seeds from tall grass. Default: True.
world.expandable-hcs=Expandable Hardcore Spawn
world.expandable-hcs.desc=Hardcore Spawn expansion based on game progression. Default: False.
world.bed-spawn-point-toggle=Bed Spawn Point
world.bed-spawn-point-toggle.desc=Permission for bed to set your spawn. This is implemented in a slightly janky way, ala fixed /setspawn. Default: False.
mobs.animageddon=Animageddon
mobs.animageddon.desc=All of the BTW's Animageddon. Default: False.
mobs.do-baby-animals-eat-loose-food=Do Baby Animals eat loose food
mobs.do-baby-animals-eat-loose-food.desc=Re-introduction of baby animal eating food off of ground. Default: False.
mobs.chicken-jockey=Chicken Jockey
mobs.chicken-jockey.desc=Buggy chicken jockeys. Default: False.
mobs.hoofsies-toggle=Hardcore Hoofsies
mobs.hoofsies-toggle.desc=Makes animals be able to kick you! This only affects the Classic+ difficulty. Default: False.
mobs.hoofsies-strength=Strength of Hoofsies
mobs.hoofsies-strength.desc=Strength multiplier of 1 makes kicking animals deal 7 HP. Strength multiplier of 0.5 makes kicking animals deal 3 HP (rounded down). This only affects the Classic+ difficulty. Default: 1.0.
synchronized.world.passable-leaves=Passable Leaves
synchronized.world.passable-leaves.desc=Ability to fall through leaves. Default: False.
synchronized.world.hcs-toggle=Hardcore Spawn for Classic+
synchronized.world.hcs-toggle.desc=This only affects the Classic+ difficulty. Default: False.
synchronized.world.vanilla-buckets=Vanillafied Buckets
synchronized.world.vanilla-buckets.desc=This makes screw pumps useless. Default: True.
synchronized.anvil.yeet-too-expensive=Yeet Too Expensive
synchronized.anvil.yeet-too-expensive.desc=Removes the Too Expensive! limit. Default: True.
synchronized.crafting.hand-planks=Planks from hand chopping
synchronized.crafting.hand-planks.desc=The amount of planks you get from just using logs on a grid. Default: 2. Range: 1-64
synchronized.crafting.stone-axe-planks=Planks from stone axe chopping
synchronized.crafting.stone-axe-planks.desc=The amount of planks you get with stone axe. Default: 3. Range: 1-64
synchronized.crafting.iron-axe-planks=Planks from iron axe chopping
synchronized.crafting.iron-axe-planks.desc=The amount of planks you get with iron or better axe. Default: 4. Range: 1-64
synchronized.crafting.saw-planks=Planks from sawing logs
synchronized.crafting.saw-planks.desc=The amount of planks you get from sawing logs. Default: 6. Range: 1-64
synchronized.silly.crafting.wicker-weaving=Wicker Weaving toggle
synchronized.silly.crafting.wicker-weaving.desc=This applies to all difficulties. Default: False.
synchronized.silly.world.hc-stump=Hardcore Stump
synchronized.silly.world.hc-stump.desc=Ability to chisel in work stumps from tree stumps. This applies to all difficulties. Default: False.